{
  "video_id": "bEdvQjTGYP8",
  "title": "We can reprogram life. How to do it wisely | Juan Enriquez",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12809.0,
      "end_time": 15142.0,
      "text": "So, there&#39;s an actor called Dustin Hoffman."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16285.0,
      "end_time": 19619.0,
      "text": "And years ago, he made this movie which some of you may have heard of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19643.0,
      "end_time": 20833.0,
      "text": "called \"The Graduate.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21261.0,
      "end_time": 23874.0,
      "text": "And there&#39;s two key scenes in that movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24559.0,
      "end_time": 26653.0,
      "text": "The first one is the seduction scene."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26677.0,
      "end_time": 28669.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not going to talk about that tonight."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28694.0,
      "end_time": 30160.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 30185.0,
      "end_time": 34775.0,
      "text": "The second scene is where he&#39;s taken out by the old guy to the pool,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34799.0,
      "end_time": 39818.0,
      "text": "and as a young college graduate, the old guy basically says one word,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39842.0,
      "end_time": 41310.0,
      "text": "just one word."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41835.0,
      "end_time": 44127.0,
      "text": "And of course, all of you know what that word is."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44151.0,
      "end_time": 45341.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s \"plastics.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45365.0,
      "end_time": 46531.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47190.0,
      "end_time": 51122.0,
      "text": "And the only problem with that is, it was completely the wrong advice."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51146.0,
      "end_time": 52633.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53229.0,
      "end_time": 55377.0,
      "text": "Let me tell you why it was so wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55401.0,
      "end_time": 57194.0,
      "text": "The word should have been \"silicon.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58163.0,
      "end_time": 60187.0,
      "text": "And the reason it should have been silicon"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60211.0,
      "end_time": 65391.0,
      "text": "is because the basic patents for semiconductors had already been made,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65416.0,
      "end_time": 66792.0,
      "text": "had already been filed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 66817.0,
      "end_time": 68582.0,
      "text": "and they were already building them."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68606.0,
      "end_time": 71693.0,
      "text": "So Silicon Valley was just being built in 1967,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71717.0,
      "end_time": 73525.0,
      "text": "when this movie was released."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 73549.0,
      "end_time": 75637.0,
      "text": "And the year after the movie was released,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 75661.0,
      "end_time": 76826.0,
      "text": "Intel was founded."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 77327.0,
      "end_time": 80152.0,
      "text": "So had the graduate heard the right one word,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 80177.0,
      "end_time": 83709.0,
      "text": "maybe he would have ended up onstage -- oh, I don&#39;t know --"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 83733.0,
      "end_time": 84891.0,
      "text": "maybe with these two."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 84915.0,
      "end_time": 87794.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 91955.0,
      "end_time": 93666.0,
      "text": "So as you&#39;re thinking of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 94626.0,
      "end_time": 98640.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s see what bit of advice we might want to give"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 98880.0,
      "end_time": 101678.0,
      "text": "so that your next graduate doesn&#39;t become a Tupperware salesman."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 101702.0,
      "end_time": 103582.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 103606.0,
      "end_time": 107351.0,
      "text": "So in 2015, what word of advice would you give people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107375.0,
      "end_time": 110160.0,
      "text": "when you took a college graduate out by the pool"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 110400.0,
      "end_time": 111930.0,
      "text": "and you said one word, just one word?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 112698.0,
      "end_time": 114698.0,
      "text": "I think the answer would be \"lifecode.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 115312.0,
      "end_time": 116471.0,
      "text": "So what is \"lifecode?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 116495.0,
      "end_time": 119232.0,
      "text": "Lifecode is the various ways we have of programming life."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 119256.0,
      "end_time": 121910.0,
      "text": "So instead of programming computers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 121115.0,
      "end_time": 123788.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re using things to program viruses"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 123812.0,
      "end_time": 125836.0,
      "text": "or retroviruses or proteins"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 125860.0,
      "end_time": 127668.0,
      "text": "or DNA or RNA"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 128501.0,
      "end_time": 131144.0,
      "text": "or plants or animals, or a whole series of creatures."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 131632.0,
      "end_time": 134162.0,
      "text": "And as you&#39;re thinking about this incredible ability"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 134186.0,
      "end_time": 136439.0,
      "text": "to make life do what you want it to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 136463.0,
      "end_time": 138579.0,
      "text": "what it&#39;s programmed to do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 138604.0,
      "end_time": 140397.0,
      "text": "what you end up doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 140421.0,
      "end_time": 143866.0,
      "text": "is taking what we&#39;ve been doing for thousands of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 143890.0,
      "end_time": 147110.0,
      "text": "which is breeding, changing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 147350.0,
      "end_time": 149106.0,
      "text": "mixing, matching"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 149130.0,
      "end_time": 151138.0,
      "text": "all kinds of life-forms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 151163.0,
      "end_time": 152624.0,
      "text": "and we accelerate it."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 152648.0,
      "end_time": 154148.0,
      "text": "And this is not something new."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 154172.0,
      "end_time": 156472.0,
      "text": "This humble mustard weed has been modified"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 157139.0,
      "end_time": 160168.0,
      "text": "so that if you change it in one way, you get broccoli."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 160714.0,
      "end_time": 163240.0,
      "text": "And if you change it in a second way, you get kale."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 163764.0,
      "end_time": 165780.0,
      "text": "And if you change it in a third way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 165804.0,
      "end_time": 167730.0,
      "text": "you get cauliflower."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 167662.0,
      "end_time": 171140.0,
      "text": "So when you go to these all-natural, organic markets,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 171380.0,
      "end_time": 172618.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re really going to a place"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 172642.0,
      "end_time": 176601.0,
      "text": "where people have been changing the lifecode of plants for a long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 177464.0,
      "end_time": 178628.0,
      "text": "The difference today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 178652.0,
      "end_time": 180897.0,
      "text": "to pick a completely politically neutral term --"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 180921.0,
      "end_time": 182612.0,
      "text": "[Intelligent design]"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 182636.0,
      "end_time": 183793.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 183817.0,
      "end_time": 186223.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re beginning to practice intelligent design."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 186819.0,
      "end_time": 189570.0,
      "text": "That means that instead of doing this at random"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 189810.0,
      "end_time": 191137.0,
      "text": "and seeing what happens over generations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 191161.0,
      "end_time": 194847.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re inserting specific genes, we&#39;re inserting specific proteins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 194871.0,
      "end_time": 198780.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re changing lifecode for very deliberate purposes."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 198745.0,
      "end_time": 201839.0,
      "text": "And that allows us to accelerate how this stuff happens."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 202473.0,
      "end_time": 204211.0,
      "text": "Let me just give you one example."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 206928.0,
      "end_time": 209823.0,
      "text": "Some of you occasionally might think about sex."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 211299.0,
      "end_time": 214528.0,
      "text": "And we kind of take it for granted how we&#39;ve changed sex."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 214552.0,
      "end_time": 217459.0,
      "text": "So we think it&#39;s perfectly normal and natural to change it."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 217960.0,
      "end_time": 220299.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s happened with sex over time is --"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 220323.0,
      "end_time": 223110.0,
      "text": "normally, sex equals baby, eventually."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 223971.0,
      "end_time": 225481.0,
      "text": "But in today&#39;s world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 225505.0,
      "end_time": 228384.0,
      "text": "sex plus pill equals no baby."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 228408.0,
      "end_time": 229892.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 229916.0,
      "end_time": 232654.0,
      "text": "And again, we think that&#39;s perfectly normal and natural,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 232678.0,
      "end_time": 235528.0,
      "text": "but that has not been the case for most of human history."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 235552.0,
      "end_time": 237203.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not the case for animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 237608.0,
      "end_time": 239590.0,
      "text": "What it is does is it gives us control,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 239614.0,
      "end_time": 242530.0,
      "text": "so sex becomes separate from conception."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 242955.0,
      "end_time": 245400.0,
      "text": "And as you&#39;re thinking of the consequences of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 245424.0,
      "end_time": 247880.0,
      "text": "then we&#39;ve been playing with stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 247112.0,
      "end_time": 249423.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s a little bit more advanced, like art."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 249447.0,
      "end_time": 251525.0,
      "text": "Not in the sense of painting and sculpture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 251549.0,
      "end_time": 256226.0,
      "text": "but in the sense of assisted reproductive technologies."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 257404.0,
      "end_time": 259840.0,
      "text": "So what are assisted reproductive technologies?"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 259865.0,
      "end_time": 263583.0,
      "text": "Assisted reproductive technologies are things like in vitro fertilization."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 264289.0,
      "end_time": 267837.0,
      "text": "And when you do in vitro fertilization, there&#39;s very good reasons to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 267862.0,
      "end_time": 270982.0,
      "text": "Sometimes you just can&#39;t conceive otherwise."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 271622.0,
      "end_time": 272777.0,
      "text": "But when you do that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 272801.0,
      "end_time": 276863.0,
      "text": "what you’re doing is separating sex, conception, baby."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 277786.0,
      "end_time": 280690.0,
      "text": "So you haven&#39;t just taken control of when you have a baby,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 280714.0,
      "end_time": 284380.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ve separated when the baby and where the baby is fertilized."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 284730.0,
      "end_time": 286922.0,
      "text": "So you&#39;ve separated the baby"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 286946.0,
      "end_time": 288651.0,
      "text": "from the body from the act."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 289332.0,
      "end_time": 292412.0,
      "text": "And as you&#39;re thinking of other things we&#39;ve been doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 292436.0,
      "end_time": 294294.0,
      "text": "think about twins."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 295290.0,
      "end_time": 297149.0,
      "text": "So you can freeze sperm, you can freeze eggs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 297173.0,
      "end_time": 298870.0,
      "text": "you can freeze fertilized eggs."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 299778.0,
      "end_time": 301543.0,
      "text": "And what does that mean?"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 301567.0,
      "end_time": 304610.0,
      "text": "Well, that&#39;s a good thing if you&#39;re a cancer patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 304850.0,
      "end_time": 307890.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re about to go under chemotherapy or under radiation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 307113.0,
      "end_time": 308343.0,
      "text": "so you save these things."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 308367.0,
      "end_time": 309604.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t irradiate them."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 310720.0,
      "end_time": 312398.0,
      "text": "But if you can save them and you can freeze them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 312422.0,
      "end_time": 314524.0,
      "text": "and you can have a surrogate mother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 314548.0,
      "end_time": 316707.0,
      "text": "it means that you&#39;ve decoupled sex from time."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 317710.0,
      "end_time": 322628.0,
      "text": "It means you can have twins born -- oh, in 50 years?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 323287.0,
      "end_time": 326976.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 327000.0,
      "end_time": 328257.0,
      "text": "In a hundred years?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 329342.0,
      "end_time": 330630.0,
      "text": "Two hundred years?"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 331566.0,
      "end_time": 334352.0,
      "text": "And these are three really profound changes"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 334377.0,
      "end_time": 335976.0,
      "text": "that are not, like, future stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 336000.0,
      "end_time": 338117.0,
      "text": "This is stuff we take for granted today."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 338911.0,
      "end_time": 341840.0,
      "text": "So this lifecode stuff turns out to be a superpower."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 342520.0,
      "end_time": 346856.0,
      "text": "It turns out to be this incredibly powerful way of changing viruses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 346880.0,
      "end_time": 349640.0,
      "text": "of changing plants, of changing animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 349840.0,
      "end_time": 352940.0,
      "text": "perhaps even of evolving ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 352118.0,
      "end_time": 355860.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s something that Steve Gullans and I have been thinking about for a while."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 356749.0,
      "end_time": 357908.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s have some risks."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 358408.0,
      "end_time": 362552.0,
      "text": "Like every powerful technology, like electricity, like an automobile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 362576.0,
      "end_time": 365885.0,
      "text": "like computers, this stuff potentially can be misused."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 366631.0,
      "end_time": 368202.0,
      "text": "And that scares a lot of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 369200.0,
      "end_time": 370784.0,
      "text": "And as you apply these technologies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 370809.0,
      "end_time": 373610.0,
      "text": "you can even turn human beings into chimeras."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 373815.0,
      "end_time": 376354.0,
      "text": "Remember the Greek myth where you mix animals?"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 376378.0,
      "end_time": 378360.0,
      "text": "Well, some of these treatments"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 378388.0,
      "end_time": 380633.0,
      "text": "actually end up changing your blood type."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 381406.0,
      "end_time": 385585.0,
      "text": "Or they&#39;ll put male cells in a female body or vice versa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 386326.0,
      "end_time": 387914.0,
      "text": "which sounds absolutely horrible"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 387938.0,
      "end_time": 390215.0,
      "text": "until you realize, the reason you&#39;re doing that"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 390239.0,
      "end_time": 393643.0,
      "text": "is you&#39;re substituting bone marrow during cancer treatments."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 393668.0,
      "end_time": 395916.0,
      "text": "So by taking somebody else&#39;s bone marrow,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 395940.0,
      "end_time": 398632.0,
      "text": "you may be changing some fundamental aspects of yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 398656.0,
      "end_time": 400544.0,
      "text": "but you&#39;re also saving your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 400568.0,
      "end_time": 402714.0,
      "text": "And as you&#39;re thinking about this stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 402738.0,
      "end_time": 404908.0,
      "text": "here&#39;s something that happened 20 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 405337.0,
      "end_time": 406861.0,
      "text": "This is Emma Ott."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 406886.0,
      "end_time": 409695.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s a recent college admittee."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 409719.0,
      "end_time": 411623.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s studying accounting."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 411648.0,
      "end_time": 415120.0,
      "text": "She played two varsity sports. She graduated as a valedictorian."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 415687.0,
      "end_time": 417707.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s not particularly extraordinary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 417731.0,
      "end_time": 421302.0,
      "text": "except that she&#39;s the first human being born to three parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 422244.0,
      "end_time": 423395.0,
      "text": "Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 423419.0,
      "end_time": 425585.0,
      "text": "Because she had a deadly mitochondrial disease"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 425609.0,
      "end_time": 427940.0,
      "text": "that she might have inherited."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 427118.0,
      "end_time": 429498.0,
      "text": "So when you swap out a third person&#39;s DNA"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 429523.0,
      "end_time": 431251.0,
      "text": "and you put it in there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 431275.0,
      "end_time": 432832.0,
      "text": "you save the lives of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 433840.0,
      "end_time": 436220.0,
      "text": "But you also are doing germline engineering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 436245.0,
      "end_time": 440388.0,
      "text": "which means her kids, if she has kids, will be saved"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 440412.0,
      "end_time": 441822.0,
      "text": "and won&#39;t go through this."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 441846.0,
      "end_time": 443337.0,
      "text": "And [their] kids will be saved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 443361.0,
      "end_time": 445195.0,
      "text": "and their grandchildren will be saved,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 445220.0,
      "end_time": 446417.0,
      "text": "and this passes on."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 446929.0,
      "end_time": 448554.0,
      "text": "That makes people nervous."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 448578.0,
      "end_time": 450928.0,
      "text": "So 20 years ago, the various authorities said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 450952.0,
      "end_time": 452871.0,
      "text": "why don&#39;t we study this for a while?"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 453903.0,
      "end_time": 457717.0,
      "text": "There are risks to doing stuff, and there are risks to not doing stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 457741.0,
      "end_time": 461890.0,
      "text": "because there were a couple dozen people saved by this technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 461113.0,
      "end_time": 464970.0,
      "text": "and then we&#39;ve been thinking about it for the next 20 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 465200.0,
      "end_time": 466185.0,
      "text": "So as we think about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 466209.0,
      "end_time": 470190.0,
      "text": "as we take the time to say, \"Hey, maybe we should have longer studies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 470430.0,
      "end_time": 472444.0,
      "text": "maybe we should do this, maybe we should do that,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 472468.0,
      "end_time": 476277.0,
      "text": "there are consequences to acting, and there are consequences to not acting."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 477203.0,
      "end_time": 478895.0,
      "text": "Like curing deadly diseases --"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 479688.0,
      "end_time": 481926.0,
      "text": "which, by the way, is completely unnatural."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 482997.0,
      "end_time": 486790.0,
      "text": "It is normal and natural for humans to be felled"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 486103.0,
      "end_time": 490172.0,
      "text": "by massive epidemics of polio, of smallpox, of tuberculosis."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 490196.0,
      "end_time": 493839.0,
      "text": "When we put vaccines into people, we are putting unnatural things"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 493863.0,
      "end_time": 495229.0,
      "text": "into their body"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 495253.0,
      "end_time": 499361.0,
      "text": "because we think the benefit outweighs the risk."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 500129.0,
      "end_time": 503842.0,
      "text": "Because we&#39;ve built unnatural plants, unnatural animals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 503866.0,
      "end_time": 506390.0,
      "text": "we can feed about seven billion people."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 506413.0,
      "end_time": 509585.0,
      "text": "We can do things like create new life-forms."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 510302.0,
      "end_time": 513819.0,
      "text": "And as you create new life-forms, again, that sounds terribly scary"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 513842.0,
      "end_time": 515524.0,
      "text": "and terribly bothersome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 515548.0,
      "end_time": 518991.0,
      "text": "until you realize that those life-forms live on your dining room table."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 519539.0,
      "end_time": 522350.0,
      "text": "Those flowers you&#39;ve got on your dining room table --"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 522590.00000000006,
      "end_time": 524228.00000000006,
      "text": "there&#39;s not a lot that&#39;s natural about them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 524253.00000000006,
      "end_time": 527345.0,
      "text": "because people have been breeding the flowers to make this color,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 527369.0,
      "end_time": 529129.0,
      "text": "to be this size, to last for a week."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 529153.0,
      "end_time": 531542.0,
      "text": "You don&#39;t usually give your loved one wildflowers"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 531566.0,
      "end_time": 534533.0,
      "text": "because they don&#39;t last a whole lot of time."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 536532.0,
      "end_time": 537770.0,
      "text": "What all this does"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 538421.0,
      "end_time": 540596.0,
      "text": "is it flips Darwin completely on his head."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 541159.0,
      "end_time": 542900.0,
      "text": "See, for four billion years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 542924.0,
      "end_time": 545989.0,
      "text": "what lived and died on this planet depended on two principles:"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 546608.0,
      "end_time": 549132.0,
      "text": "on natural selection and random mutation."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 550160.0,
      "end_time": 552642.0,
      "text": "And so what lived and died, what was structured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 553167.0,
      "end_time": 554850.0,
      "text": "has now been flipped on its head."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 556262.0,
      "end_time": 557460.0,
      "text": "And what we&#39;ve done"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 557485.0,
      "end_time": 560960.0,
      "text": "is created this completely parallel evolutionary system"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 560120.0,
      "end_time": 563449.0,
      "text": "where we are practicing unnatural selection and non-random mutation."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 563473.0,
      "end_time": 565168.0,
      "text": "So let me explain these things."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 565192.0,
      "end_time": 566581.0,
      "text": "This is natural selection."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 567900.0,
      "end_time": 568495.0,
      "text": "This is unnatural selection."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 568519.0,
      "end_time": 571141.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 571903.0,
      "end_time": 574547.0,
      "text": "So what happens with this stuff is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 574571.0,
      "end_time": 577285.0,
      "text": "we started breeding wolves thousands of years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 577309.0,
      "end_time": 579499.0,
      "text": "in central Asia to turn them into dogs."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 579523.0,
      "end_time": 581817.0,
      "text": "And then we started turning them into big dogs"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 581841.0,
      "end_time": 583592.0,
      "text": "and into little dogs."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 583616.0,
      "end_time": 585403.0,
      "text": "But if you take one of the chihuahuas"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 585427.0,
      "end_time": 588275.0,
      "text": "you see in the Hermès bags on Fifth Avenue"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 588299.0,
      "end_time": 590956.0,
      "text": "and you let it loose on the African plain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 590980.0,
      "end_time": 592964.0,
      "text": "you can watch natural selection happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 592988.0,
      "end_time": 595669.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 598419.0,
      "end_time": 601236.0,
      "text": "Few things on Earth are less natural than a cornfield."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 602188.0,
      "end_time": 605761.0,
      "text": "You will never, under any scenario, walk through a virgin forest"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 605785.0,
      "end_time": 608469.0,
      "text": "and see the same plant growing in orderly rows"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 608494.0,
      "end_time": 609818.0,
      "text": "at the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 609842.0,
      "end_time": 611453.0,
      "text": "nothing else living there."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 612398.0,
      "end_time": 613557.0,
      "text": "When you do a cornfield,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 613581.0,
      "end_time": 615628.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re selecting what lives and what dies."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 616800.0,
      "end_time": 618419.0,
      "text": "And you&#39;re doing that through unnatural selection."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 618443.0,
      "end_time": 621579.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the same with a wheat field, it&#39;s the same with a rice field."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 621604.0,
      "end_time": 624219.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the same with a city, it&#39;s the same with a suburb."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 624243.0,
      "end_time": 626138.0,
      "text": "In fact, half the surface of Earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 626162.0,
      "end_time": 627669.0,
      "text": "has been unnaturally engineered"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 627693.0,
      "end_time": 630876.0,
      "text": "so that what lives and what dies there is what we want,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 630900.0,
      "end_time": 633363.0,
      "text": "which is the reason why you don&#39;t have grizzly bears"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 633387.0,
      "end_time": 635314.0,
      "text": "walking through downtown Manhattan."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 637770.0,
      "end_time": 638936.0,
      "text": "How about this random mutation stuff?"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 638960.0,
      "end_time": 640403.0,
      "text": "Well, this is random mutation."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 640427.0,
      "end_time": 641767.0,
      "text": "This is Antonio Alfonseca."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 642350.0,
      "end_time": 645610.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s otherwise known as the Octopus, his nickname."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 645850.0,
      "end_time": 647359.0,
      "text": "He was the Relief Pitcher of the Year in 2000."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 647955.0,
      "end_time": 650719.0,
      "text": "And he had a random mutation that gave him six fingers"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 650743.0,
      "end_time": 652971.0,
      "text": "on each hand,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 652995.0,
      "end_time": 655637.0,
      "text": "which turns out to be really useful if you&#39;re a pitcher."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 655661.0,
      "end_time": 657300.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 658119.0,
      "end_time": 659849.0,
      "text": "How about non-random mutation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 660415.0,
      "end_time": 663387.0,
      "text": "A non-random mutation is beer."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 663412.0,
      "end_time": 665110.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s wine. It&#39;s yogurt."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 665928.0,
      "end_time": 668264.0,
      "text": "How many times have you walked through the forest"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 668288.0,
      "end_time": 669851.0,
      "text": "and found all-natural cheese?"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 670859.0,
      "end_time": 672102.0,
      "text": "Or all-natural yogurt?"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 673460.0,
      "end_time": 674831.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve been engineering this stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 674855.0,
      "end_time": 676323.0,
      "text": "Now, the interesting thing is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 676347.0,
      "end_time": 677965.0,
      "text": "we get to know the stuff better."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 678364.0,
      "end_time": 682770.0,
      "text": "We found one of the single most powerful gene-editing instruments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 682101.0,
      "end_time": 683888.0,
      "text": "CRISPR, inside yogurt."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 685280.0,
      "end_time": 687180.0,
      "text": "And as we start engineering cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 687420.0,
      "end_time": 691322.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re producing eight out of the top 10 pharmaceutical products,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 692246.0,
      "end_time": 694771.0,
      "text": "including the stuff that you use to treat arthritis,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 694795.0,
      "end_time": 697221.0,
      "text": "which is the number one best-selling drug, Humira."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 697985.0,
      "end_time": 699436.0,
      "text": "So this lifecode stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 700229.0,
      "end_time": 701605.0,
      "text": "It really is a superpower."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 702156.0,
      "end_time": 704690.0,
      "text": "It really is a way of programming stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 704940.0,
      "end_time": 706651.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s nothing that&#39;s going to change us"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 706675.0,
      "end_time": 708800.0,
      "text": "more than this lifecode."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 709597.0,
      "end_time": 711578.0,
      "text": "So as you&#39;re thinking of lifecode,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 711602.0,
      "end_time": 713290.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s think of five principles"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 714231.0,
      "end_time": 716860.0,
      "text": "as to how we start guiding,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 716110.0,
      "end_time": 717729.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;d love you to give me more."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 718315.0,
      "end_time": 719817.0,
      "text": "So, principle number one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 720282.0,
      "end_time": 722425.0,
      "text": "we have to take responsibility for this stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 723420.0,
      "end_time": 725593.0,
      "text": "The reason we have to take responsibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 725617.0,
      "end_time": 726978.0,
      "text": "is because we&#39;re in charge."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 727200.0,
      "end_time": 728915.0,
      "text": "These aren&#39;t random mutations."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 728939.0,
      "end_time": 731242.0,
      "text": "This is what we are doing, what we are choosing."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 731266.0,
      "end_time": 732964.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not, \"Stuff happened.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 732989.0,
      "end_time": 734462.0,
      "text": "It didn&#39;t happen at random."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 734486.0,
      "end_time": 737900.0,
      "text": "It didn&#39;t come down by a verdict of somebody else."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 737114.0,
      "end_time": 738931.0,
      "text": "We engineer this stuff,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 738955.0,
      "end_time": 742200.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s the Pottery Barn rule: you break it, you own it."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 742962.0,
      "end_time": 744491.0,
      "text": "Principle number two:"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 744515.0,
      "end_time": 747643.0,
      "text": "we have to recognize and celebrate diversity in this stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 747667.0,
      "end_time": 750801.0,
      "text": "There have been at least 33 versions of hominids"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 750825.0,
      "end_time": 752547.0,
      "text": "that have walked around this Earth."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 752912.0,
      "end_time": 755218.0,
      "text": "Most all of them went extinct except us."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 755804.0,
      "end_time": 757964.0,
      "text": "But the normal and natural state of this Earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 757989.0,
      "end_time": 761376.0,
      "text": "is we have various versions of humans walking around at the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 761400.0,
      "end_time": 764570.0,
      "text": "which is why most of us have some Neanderthal in us."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 764559.0,
      "end_time": 766999.0,
      "text": "Some of us have some Denisova in us."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 767230.0,
      "end_time": 769372.0,
      "text": "And some in Washington have a lot more of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 769396.0,
      "end_time": 771973.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 771998.0,
      "end_time": 773883.0,
      "text": "Principle number three:"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 773907.0,
      "end_time": 776720.0,
      "text": "we have to respect other people&#39;s choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 776608.0,
      "end_time": 778882.0,
      "text": "Some people will choose to never alter."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 778907.0,
      "end_time": 780717.0,
      "text": "Some people will choose to alter all."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 780741.0,
      "end_time": 783367.0,
      "text": "Some people will choose to alter plants but not animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 783391.0,
      "end_time": 785442.0,
      "text": "Some people will choose to alter themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 785466.0,
      "end_time": 787729.0,
      "text": "Some people will choose to evolve themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 787753.0,
      "end_time": 789322.0,
      "text": "Diversity is not a bad thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 789346.0,
      "end_time": 791988.0,
      "text": "because even though we think of humans as very diverse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 792120.0,
      "end_time": 794296.0,
      "text": "we came so close to extinction"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 794321.0,
      "end_time": 796936.0,
      "text": "that all of us descend from a single African mother"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 796960.0,
      "end_time": 798285.0,
      "text": "and the consequence of that"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 798309.0,
      "end_time": 802814.0,
      "text": "is there&#39;s more genetic diversity in 55 African chimpanzees"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 802838.0,
      "end_time": 804713.0,
      "text": "than there are in seven billion humans."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 806254.0,
      "end_time": 808256.0,
      "text": "Principle number four:"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 809790.0,
      "end_time": 811790.0,
      "text": "we should take about a quarter of the Earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 811780.0,
      "end_time": 814600.0,
      "text": "and only let Darwin run the show there."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 814981.0,
      "end_time": 816582.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t have to be contiguous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 816606.0,
      "end_time": 818380.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t have to all be tied together."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 818404.0,
      "end_time": 820610.0,
      "text": "It should be part in the oceans, part on land."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 820634.0,
      "end_time": 824170.0,
      "text": "But we should not run every evolutionary decision on this planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 824474.0,
      "end_time": 826912.0,
      "text": "We want to have our evolutionary system running."
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 826936.0,
      "end_time": 829513.0,
      "text": "We want to have Darwin&#39;s evolutionary system running."
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 829537.0,
      "end_time": 833213.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s just really important to have these two things running in parallel"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 833237.0,
      "end_time": 834754.0,
      "text": "and not overwhelm evolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 834778.0,
      "end_time": 838888.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 842307.0,
      "end_time": 843701.0,
      "text": "Last thing I&#39;ll say."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 844654.0,
      "end_time": 847915.0,
      "text": "This is the single most exciting adventure human beings have been on."
    },
    {
      "index": 313,
      "start_time": 847940.0,
      "end_time": 850981.0,
      "text": "This is the single greatest superpower humans have ever had."
    },
    {
      "index": 314,
      "start_time": 851500.0,
      "end_time": 853873.0,
      "text": "It would be a crime for you not to participate in this stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 315,
      "start_time": 853897.0,
      "end_time": 855309.0,
      "text": "because you&#39;re scared of it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 316,
      "start_time": 855333.0,
      "end_time": 857720.0,
      "text": "because you&#39;re hiding from it."
    },
    {
      "index": 317,
      "start_time": 857960.0,
      "end_time": 860467.0,
      "text": "You can participate in the ethics. You can participate in the politics."
    },
    {
      "index": 318,
      "start_time": 860491.0,
      "end_time": 862240.0,
      "text": "You can participate in the business."
    },
    {
      "index": 319,
      "start_time": 862264.0,
      "end_time": 865422.0,
      "text": "You can participate in just thinking about where medicine is going,"
    },
    {
      "index": 320,
      "start_time": 865446.0,
      "end_time": 866607.0,
      "text": "where industry is going,"
    },
    {
      "index": 321,
      "start_time": 866631.0,
      "end_time": 868434.0,
      "text": "where we&#39;re going to take the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 322,
      "start_time": 868458.0,
      "end_time": 870323.0,
      "text": "It would be a crime for all of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 323,
      "start_time": 870347.0,
      "end_time": 874405.0,
      "text": "not to be aware when somebody shows up at a swimming pool"
    },
    {
      "index": 324,
      "start_time": 874429.0,
      "end_time": 877700.0,
      "text": "and says one word, just one word,"
    },
    {
      "index": 325,
      "start_time": 877499.0,
      "end_time": 879898.0,
      "text": "if you don&#39;t listen if that word is \"lifecode.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 326,
      "start_time": 879922.0,
      "end_time": 881200.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 327,
      "start_time": 881224.0,
      "end_time": 888437.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}